      <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">G</div><div><div class="review-name">George</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
    </article>
    <article class="review-card">
      <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
      <p class="review-quote">"The results are amazing. Clicks, impressions, and my average position have all improved significantly. People are finding me through Google more than ever before, and the investment is paying off big time."</p>
      <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">AS</div><div><div class="review-name">Audrey Schoen, LMFT</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
    </article>
    <article class="review-card">
      <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
      <p class="review-quote">"If you are a therapist looking for SEO strategy and implementation, Chris and his Moonraker team know how to rank you high on Google. I highly recommend them."</p>
      <div class="review-author"><div class="review-avatar">BS</div><div><div class="review-name">Brent Stutzman</div><div class="review-meta">Google review</div></div></div>
